metadata.name: The Great Depression
metadata.description:
The Great Depression is a 1/1 NFT created by artist VLH as a response to the ongoing economical crisis. The reference to the great depression of 1929-1932 shows laborers wandering around and struggeling. 
The background gives an extra dimension to the digital artwork and provides a sence of desolution with not only despair but also a 'no way out'.
